org.trippi

Class TupleIterator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.trippi.TupleIterator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TrippiIterator<Map<String,org.jrdf.graph.Node>>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CountTupleIterator, DistinctTupleIterator, LimitedTupleIterator, PoolAwareTupleIterator, SparqlTupleIterator, SynchronizedTupleIterator

    public abstract class TupleIterator
extends Object
implements TrippiIterator<Map<String,org.jrdf.graph.Node>>
    An iterator over a series of tuples. Each tuple is a Map of JRDF Node objects keyed by query binding variable names.
    Author:
    cwilper@cs.cornell.edu
